<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />I am weary with my crying; my throat is dry;</para>

<para style="q1">my eyes fail while I wait for my God.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />Those who hate me without a cause are more than the hairs on my head;</para>

<para style="q1">those who would cut me off, being my enemies for wrong reasons, are mighty;</para>

<para style="q1">what I did not steal, I have to give back.</para>
